### Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "password": "demo"
}

### Upload (set Authorization: Bearer {{token}})
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tmx/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

--WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tmx"; filename="sample.tmx"
Content-Type: application/xml

<@ ./sample.tmx
--WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Update TU
POST http://localhost:3000/api/tmx/{{tmxId}}/update
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tuIndex": 0,
  "lang": "pt-BR",
  "text": "Olá, universo!"
}

### Export
GET http://localhost:3000/api/tmx/{{tmxId}}/export
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
